Some of them are also having different root like American, Canadian, Afghanistan, German, French, Italian, etc. See the list below in no particular order or ranking.

Her film credits include Imagine That, Smallfoot, and the lead role in The Sun Is Also a Star. Her father is an Iranian.

Born: 10 February 2000, Minneapolis, Minnesota, United States

Height: 1.6 m

Parents: Afshin Shahidi, Keri Shahidi

Education: Dwight Global Online School, Harvard University

Siblings: Sayeed Shahidi, Ehsan Shahidi

Movies and TV shows: Grown-ish (Since 2018), Black-ish (Since 2014), The Sun Is Also a Star (2019), Imagine That (2009), Smallfoot (2018)
